            </title>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<div class="tougao-user">感谢 IT 之家网友 <a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1168596" rel="nofollow">手可摘星辰</a>、<a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D284961" rel="nofollow">Hassy</a>、<a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1478139" rel="nofollow">ThreeDrops_Water</a>、<a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1267235" rel="nofollow">去繁就简</a>、<a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1234925" rel="nofollow">墨笙</a>、<a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D931763" rel="nofollow">陈雨晨</a>、<a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1860885" rel="nofollow">青衫磊落 zck</a>、<a href="https://m.ithome.com/html/app/open.html?url=ithome%3A%2F%2Fuserpage%3Fid%3D1119148" rel="nofollow">jingyu_</a> 的线索投递！</div><p data-vmark="93b2">13:52 更新：喜马拉雅官方微博表示，<span class="accentTextColor">目前已紧急修复，不会影响大家的会员等权益</span>。</p><p data-vmark="ccc3" style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2023/12/aeae7ff8-26db-4392-b68f-8d6f339f7edd.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" w="785" h="265" title="（更新：已修复）「喜马拉雅崩了」登上热搜，网友误以为是「山崩了」" width="785" height="265" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p data-vmark="c031"><a class="s_tag" href="https://www.ithome.com/" target="_blank">IT 之家</a> 12 月 19 日消息，据多位 IT 之家小伙伴投稿，喜马拉雅 App 出现服务问题，<span class="accentTextColor">在有会员的情况下依然提示购买才能播放</span>，还会出现 502 错误。</p><p data-vmark="fdd8" style="text-align: center;"><span class="post-img-item"><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2023/12/fb5fe638-e1c7-494e-8603-7f177b1b7a63.png?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xYy9xYzE1OS5wbmc=,t_100,g_3,y_16,x_16,a_0/format,f_auto" title="（更新：已修复）「喜马拉雅崩了」登上热搜，网友误以为是「山崩了」" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span></p><p data-vmark="f8aa" style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2023/12/05422a42-ffc8-4b05-828b-f2a609a9eeb3.png?x-bce-process=image/watermark,image_aW1nL3dhdGVybWFyay9xYy9xYzg5LnBuZw==,t_100,g_6,y_10,x_9,a_0/format,f_auto" w="576" h="1186" title="（更新：已修复）「喜马拉雅崩了」登上热搜，网友误以为是「山崩了」" width="576" height="1186" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p data-vmark="4446" style="text-align: justify;"><span class="post-img-item"></span>截至 IT 之家发稿，<span class="accentTextColor">「喜马拉雅崩了」已排名微博热搜第二</span>，然而不少网友表示是被「骗进来」的，误以为是地震导致「喜马拉雅山崩了」。</p><p data-vmark="fade" style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2023/12/359368a5-fd73-46fc-a3e0-ce9323f7e3d3.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" w="351" h="96" title="（更新：已修复）「喜马拉雅崩了」登上热搜，网友误以为是「山崩了」" width="351" height="96" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p data-vmark="b0b8" style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2023/12/5fb1d28f-836d-4049-a90a-bf47448df740.png?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" w="809" h="955" title="（更新：已修复）「喜马拉雅崩了」登上热搜，网友误以为是「山崩了」" width="809" height="955" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p data-vmark="a59c">喜马拉雅是一家音频分享平台，汇集了有声小说、儿童故事、相声评书、京剧戏曲、新闻段子、广播电台等音频内容。</p><p class="ad-tips">广告声明：文内含有的对外跳转链接（包括不限于超链接、二维码、口令等形式），用于传递更多信息，节省甄选时间，结果仅供参考，IT 之家所有文章均包含本声明。</p>
